{"id": "art-3151", "label": "Art. 3151", "title": "Art. 3151: Subconcesionarea", "slug": "art-3151", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_12843119\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1411\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_12843119\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 315<sup>1</sup>:\nSubconcesionarea </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1603512030\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1410\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1603512030\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Prin excep&#355;ie de la prevederile art. 303, ale art.\n305 alin. (1) &#351;i ale art. 310 alin. (3) lit. d), companiile\nna&#355;ionale, societ&#259;&#355;ile na&#355;ionale sau societ&#259;&#355;ile\ncomerciale prev&#259;zute la art. 315 alin. (1) pot subconcesiona bunurile\nproprietate public&#259; care le-au fost concesionate potrivit art. 315 alin.\n(1).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2009333534\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1409\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2009333534\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Studiul de oportunitate al subconcesion&#259;rii se\naprob&#259; de c&#259;tre entit&#259;&#355;ile care, potrivit art. 303, au\ncalitatea de concedent în contractul de concesiune.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1594458930\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1408\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1594458930\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Subconcesionarea prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (1) se\naprob&#259;, pe baza studiului de oportunitate, prin hot&#259;râre a\nGuvernului, a consiliilor locale, jude&#355;ene sau a Consiliului General al\nMunicipiului Bucure&#351;ti, dup&#259; caz.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1931262180\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1407\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1931262180\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)F&#259;r&#259; a aduce atingere prevederilor alin. (2)\n&#351;i (3), regimul juridic al subconcesion&#259;rii prev&#259;zute la alin.\n(1) este cel instituit de prezentul cod pentru concesionare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_136202669\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1406\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_136202669\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Prin excep&#355;ie de la prevederile art. 307 alin. (1)\n&#351;i (2), redeven&#355;a ob&#355;inut&#259; prin subconcesionare se face\nvenit la bugetul companiilor na&#355;ionale, societ&#259;&#355;ilor\nna&#355;ionale sau societ&#259;&#355;ilor comerciale care au subconcesionat\nbunurile apar&#355;inând propriet&#259;&#355;ii publice.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1154741066\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1405\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1154741066\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Sumele reprezentând redeven&#355;a prev&#259;zut&#259;\nla alin. (5) sunt utilizate numai pentru între&#355;inerea, repararea,\nreabilitarea, modernizarea &#351;i/sau dezvoltarea bunurilor proprietate\npublic&#259; care au f&#259;cut obiectul concesion&#259;rii &#351;i nu pot fi\nrecuperate prin amortizare conform prevederilor legale în vigoare.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}